create_time.description: Output only. The creation time of the catalog. A timestamp in RFC3339 UTC "Zulu" format, with nanosecond resolution and up to nine fractional digits.

delete_time.description: Output only. The deletion time of the catalog. Only set after the catalog is deleted. A timestamp in RFC3339 UTC "Zulu" format, with nanosecond resolution and up to nine fractional digits.

expire_time.description: Output only. The time when this catalog is considered expired. Only set after the catalog is deleted. Only set after the catalog is deleted. A timestamp in RFC3339 UTC "Zulu" format, with nanosecond resolution and up to nine fractional digits.

location.description: The geographic location where the Catalog should reside.

name.description: The name of the Catalog. Format: projects/{project_id_or_number}/locations/{locationId}/catalogs/{catalogId}

update_time.description: Output only. The last modification time of the catalog. A timestamp in RFC3339 UTC "Zulu" format, with nanosecond resolution and up to nine fractional digits.
